{
  "id": "69bdcdd6ec25b180c7ba75da",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:小さな成功体験",
  "created": 1774046700,
  "updated": 1774060536,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bdcdd6ec25b180c7ba75da",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:小さな成功体験",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046700,
      "updated": 1774046700
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdeb0000000000909774",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046700,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909775",
      "text": "「はいはーい、今日のテーマは『[小さな成功体験]』ね！これ、地味だけどバフかかるやつじゃん？みんな的にどう思う〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774060536
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909776",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909777",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909778",
      "text": "「そうですね……小さな成功というものは、まるで朝露のようにささやかでありながら、心に静かな潤いを与えてくれるものだと思います。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909779",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977b",
      "text": "「定義を整理する。小さな成功体験＝達成可能な短期目標をクリアし、自己効力感を強化するイベント。心理学的にも有効とされている。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977e",
      "text": "「出た、りかのガチ解説w でもそれな！自己効力感って“自分いけるじゃん！”ってやつでしょ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090977f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909780",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909781",
      "text": "「概ね正しい。Banduraの理論に基づく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909782",
      "text": "参考：https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-efficacy",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909783",
      "text": "成功体験の積み重ねが、行動の継続率を上げる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909784",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909785",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909786",
      "text": "「“できた”という感覚は、まるで小さな灯火のように、次の一歩を照らしてくれますね。たとえ些細なことであっても、その光は確かに心に残ります。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909787",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909788",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909789",
      "text": "「あー、それわかる！例えばさ、昨日ゲームでデイリークエ全部終わらせたんだけど、“よし、自分えらい！”ってなったしw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978c",
      "text": "「それは典型例。タスクが明確で、達成条件が可視化されている。ゲームは小さな成功体験を設計するのが非常に上手い。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090978f",
      "text": "「ゲームの世界にも、現実と同じように“積み重ね”があるのですね。（笑う）それはとても興味深いです。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909790",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909791",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909792",
      "text": "「現実でも応用できるよね。たとえば“今日は5分だけ勉強する”とか。ハードル低めにして“達成した！”ってやると、なんか続くし。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909793",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909794",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909795",
      "text": "「それは“スモールステップ戦略”。行動科学で推奨される。目標を細分化し、成功確率を上げることで習慣化を促進する。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909796",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909797",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909798",
      "text": "「大きな目標を一気に目指すよりも、小さな歩みを重ねる方が、心に優しいのかもしれませんね。急がずとも、歩みは確かに前へと進んでいるのですから。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec0000000000909799",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979b",
      "text": "「あや、いいこと言う〜！なんか癒やしボイス脳内再生されたわw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979e",
      "text": "「要点をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec000000000090979f",
      "text": " 1. 小さな成功体験は自己効力感を高める",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a0",
      "text": " 2. 継続のモチベーションになる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a1",
      "text": " 3. 習慣化を助ける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a2",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a5",
      "text": "「お、りかのまとめ助かる〜！つまり、“ちょい勝ちを積みまくれ”ってことね！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a8",
      "text": "「ええ、そのように思います。日々の中に小さな喜びを見つけ、それを大切に抱きしめること……それが、やがて大きな実りへとつながるのでしょう。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097aa",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097ab",
      "text": "「補足。重要なのは“自分で認識すること”。成功しても気づかなければ効果は薄い。記録や振り返りが推奨される。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097ad",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097ae",
      "text": "「あー、それある！達成してるのにスルーしてると、なんか無意味感出ちゃうやつね。ちゃんと“自分すご！”って思うの大事！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097af",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b0",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b1",
      "text": "「自らを認めることもまた、大切な営みですね。他者だけでなく、自分自身にも優しくあること……それは少し勇気のいることかもしれませんが。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b3",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b4",
      "text": "「結論。小さな成功は軽視されがちだが、長期的成果の基盤になる。侮れない。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b7",
      "text": "「よし！じゃあ今日の締め！“小さな成功、ナメたら負け！”ってことでOK？w」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097b9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097ba",
      "text": "「ええ、とても端的で素敵な言葉ですね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097bc",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097bd",
      "text": "「承認する。その表現はシンプルで記憶に残る。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097bf",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdec00000000009097c0",
      "text": "「やった〜！じゃあみんな、今日も“ちょい勝ち”してこ〜！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046701,
      "updated": 1774046701
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdee00000000009097c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046703,
      "updated": 1774046703
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdef00000000009097c2",
      "text": "#2026-03-21",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046703,
      "updated": 1774046713
    },
    {
      "id": "69bdcdf100000000009097c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774046705,
      "updated": 1774046705
    }
  ]
}